<title>Files &amp; data access</title>

<p><link xref="tech-gio">GIO</link> is a high-level VFS (virtual filesystem) API. It can be used to asynchronously read and write files, as well as other data streams. GIO also provides utilities such as icons and application launching</p>

<p><link xref="tech-tracker">Tracker</link> is metadata database. It can be used to store and retrieve document metadata, as well as structured data, such as contacts.</p>

